00:33:29,734 --> 00:33:33,034
Who said you could see Do Ra?

524
00:33:33,034 --> 00:33:35,504
Huh? Where are you going right now?

525
00:33:35,504 --> 00:33:37,174
Are you going to see that girl again?

526
00:33:37,174 --> 00:33:39,534
She says she doesn't like you!

527
00:33:42,074 --> 00:33:46,054
Do Ra, I heard you met my mom.

528
00:33:46,054 --> 00:33:47,774
I'm so sorry.

529
00:33:47,774 --> 00:33:50,614
You must've been stunned because of her.

530
00:33:51,614 --> 00:33:53,214
Yes.

531
00:33:54,214 --> 00:33:58,464
She thought you and I were dating.

532
00:33:58,464 --> 00:34:00,484
We're not like that.

533
00:34:00,484 --> 00:34:05,124
So, I told her that I'm not interested in you romantically at all.

534
00:34:05,124 --> 00:34:07,174
What do you mean?

535
00:34:08,024 --> 00:34:10,774
I thought we were getting started.

536
00:34:10,774 --> 00:34:12,294
Pardon?

537
00:34:13,754 --> 00:34:16,694
What do you mean, President Gong?

538
00:34:16,694 --> 00:34:18,624
When did we...

539
00:34:18,624 --> 00:34:21,804
I never thought that even once.

540
00:34:27,604 --> 00:34:30,114
I'm a bit shocked.

541
00:34:31,924 --> 00:34:36,894
If so, why did you see a musical with me

542
00:34:36,894 --> 00:34:40,204
