548
00:35:01,594 --> 00:35:04,264
And the musical...

549
00:35:07,914 --> 00:35:10,944
My mom suddenly got an upset stomach.

550
00:35:10,944 --> 00:35:13,664
So, I had no choice but to see it with you alone.

551
00:35:13,664 --> 00:35:16,804
I didn't think of it as a date.

552
00:35:16,804 --> 00:35:19,084
And I told my mom to return the necklace.

553
00:35:19,084 --> 00:35:21,984
So, I thought she returned it to you.

554
00:35:22,714 --> 00:35:26,334
I'll check again if you haven't received it.

555
00:35:30,104 --> 00:35:35,774
I'm sorry if I mistakenly led you on.

556
00:35:35,774 --> 00:35:37,334
So...

557
00:35:38,234 --> 00:35:42,194
you mean I've been imagining things on my own?

558
00:35:42,194 --> 00:35:44,444
I'll be careful from now on, too.

559
00:35:44,444 --> 00:35:47,354
I hope this doesn't happen again.

560
00:35:49,004 --> 00:35:51,404
I'll get going now.

561
00:35:59,684 --> 00:36:03,594
Gosh, why return something so pretty?

562
00:36:03,594 --> 00:36:08,934
