563
00:36:08,934 --> 00:36:11,904
That way, I could survive.

564
00:36:22,094 --> 00:36:25,024
Yes, it's me.

565
00:36:25,024 --> 00:36:29,514
What? All the members are there?

566
00:36:43,784 --> 00:36:45,934
Make a decision.

567
00:36:50,094 --> 00:36:51,554
Three.

568
00:36:51,554 --> 00:36:54,024
- Call. 
 - Three. Call.

569
00:36:55,264 --> 00:36:58,024
Boss, please show your cards.

570
00:37:02,784 --> 00:37:04,154
Straight.

571
00:37:04,154 --> 00:37:05,744
Here we go.

572
00:37:05,744 --> 00:37:07,824
Flush. Win.

573
00:37:17,290 --> 00:37:18,980
Here.

574
00:37:23,004 --> 00:37:26,364
Brother, when did I ever wear fake ones?

575
00:37:26,364 --> 00:37:28,744
Stop touching it and give me money right now.

576
00:37:28,744 --> 00:37:31,104
Okay, I'll get it for you now.

577
00:37:48,394 --> 00:37:50,144
Baek Mi Ja...

