589
00:38:32,964 --> 00:38:34,344
Me?

590
00:38:34,344 --> 00:38:37,904
I'm out to see a friend. Why?

591
00:38:37,904 --> 00:38:41,565
Didn't you return the necklace to President Gong?

592
00:38:41,565 --> 00:38:44,625
Well, I-I have it. I have it.

593
00:38:44,625 --> 00:38:46,685
Why? I-I've been a bit busy.

594
00:38:46,685 --> 00:38:48,805
I told you to return it immediately.

595
00:38:48,805 --> 00:38:50,815
Why didn't you return it yet?

596
00:38:50,815 --> 00:38:55,225
