597
00:38:55,225 --> 00:38:57,145
What?

598
00:38:57,145 --> 00:39:00,955
President Gong's mom came to see you? Why?

599
00:39:00,955 --> 00:39:04,365
She told me to break up with him, thinking we were dating.

600
00:39:04,365 --> 00:39:07,005
She told me to get lost.

601
00:39:07,005 --> 00:39:10,105
Why do I have to hear that from his mom?

602
00:39:10,105 --> 00:39:13,485
D-Do Ra, so what did you tell her?

603
00:39:13,485 --> 00:39:14,995
What do you think?

604
00:39:14,995 --> 00:39:17,295
I said I'm not interested in him at all

605
00:39:17,295 --> 00:39:20,185
and I made it clear that there was nothing going on.

606
00:39:20,185 --> 00:39:23,865
So you'd better return that necklace quickly, okay?

607
00:39:23,865 --> 00:39:26,365
H-Hey, D-Do... Do...

608
00:39:29,265 --> 00:39:30,775
What do I do?  What do I do?

609
00:39:30,775 --> 00:39:32,915
What do I do?

610
00:39:35,075 --> 00:39:38,455
It's President Gong. Gosh. 
    

