614
00:39:50,365 --> 00:39:53,335
 He's calling me "President Baek" instead of "Mother" now. 

615
00:39:53,335 --> 00:39:55,325
 He must be really upset. 

616
00:39:55,325 --> 00:39:56,955
 What do I do? 

617
00:39:56,955 --> 00:40:00,185
 No, Baek Mi Ja. Stay alert. 

618
00:40:00,185 --> 00:40:03,205
 Even if you get dragged into a tiger cave, you can survive by staying alert. 

619
00:40:03,205 --> 00:40:05,675
President Gong, the thing is—

620
00:40:05,675 --> 00:40:09,765
You told me that Do Ra was interested in me, too.

621
00:40:09,765 --> 00:40:12,005
But she said she wasn't.

622
00:40:12,005 --> 00:40:14,675
She says she's not interested in me at all.

623
00:40:15,565 --> 00:40:18,385
I heard she asked you to return the necklace, too.

624
00:40:18,385 --> 00:40:26,305
That's why you shouldn't have let your mother go meet Do Ra.

625
00:40:26,305 --> 00:40:27,425
Pardon?

626
00:40:27,425 --> 00:40:30,525
Do Ra has never been involved in a scandal.

627
00:40:30,525 --> 00:40:34,065
As you know, since she's proud and strict to herself,

628
00:40:34,065 --> 00:40:37,465
she doesn't easily fall for anyone.

629
00:40:37,465 --> 00:40:42,465
But she went to see a musical with you alone.

630
00:40:42,465 --> 00:40:48,015
In my opinion, she did have feelings for you.

631
00:40:48,015 --> 00:40:51,105
If only your mother didn't flip out today,

632
00:40:51,105 --> 00:40:57,845
I'm sure Do Ra would've opened up herself more to you.

633
00:40:58,985 --> 00:41:01,965
If so, is it because of my mother—

634
00:41:01,965 --> 00:41:06,515
My Do Ra is an A-list actor in the country. A-list.

635
00:41:06,515 --> 00:41:09,025
Try thinking from her perspective.

636
00:41:09,025 --> 00:41:12,415
She has a lot of pride. Imagine how hurt she must've been.

637
00:41:12,415 --> 00:41:14,565
How devastated she must've been?

638
00:41:14,565 --> 00:41:19,275
Even I feel so disappointed with you now.

639
00:41:20,405 --> 00:41:24,435
I'm sorry. T-That didn't cross my mind at all.

640
00:41:24,435 --> 00:41:27,095
Could you tell Do Ra...

641
00:41:28,565 --> 00:41:30,725
What do I do now?

642
00:41:33,995 --> 00:41:38,765
I think it'd only backfire if you apologize now.

643
00:41:39,805 --> 00:41:43,045
Why don't you wait a bit for now?

644
00:41:43,045 --> 00:41:47,655
I'll try to persuade Do Ra this time, too.

645
00:41:47,655 --> 00:41:49,815
Could you really do that?

646
00:41:49,815 --> 00:41:51,485
Thank you, Mother.

647
00:41:51,485 --> 00:41:53,965
I'm indebted to you again.

648
00:41:54,965 --> 00:41:58,555
Right, by the way, the necklace...

649
00:41:58,555 --> 00:42:05,285
Let's just say you got it back for now.

650
00:42:05,285 --> 00:42:11,555
I'll give it to Do Ra once she feels better.

651
00:42:11,555 --> 00:42:13,495
Oh, okay, okay.

652
00:42:13,495 --> 00:42:17,755
My mother will not be seeing her again.

653
00:42:17,755 --> 00:42:22,325
So, please don't be angry and forgive me just once.

654
00:42:22,325 --> 00:42:24,115
I beg you, Mother.

655
00:42:24,115 --> 00:42:30,505
Gosh, seriously. I'm so upset right now.

656
00:42:32,115 --> 00:42:35,905
 Gosh, that was a close one. Seriously. 

657
00:42:41,065 --> 00:42:45,025
Do Ra, Do Ra, drink this before you go.

658
00:42:45,025 --> 00:42:46,735
What's this?

659
00:42:46,735 --> 00:42:51,935
I made honey tea with pear, jujube, and bellflower root. Drink up. Drink up.

660
00:42:53,765 --> 00:42:58,025
Oh, right. You returned the necklace President Gong gave me, right?

661
00:42:58,025 --> 00:43:02,245
Yes, I gave it back. You told me to.

662
00:43:05,125 --> 00:43:08,935
Do Ra, I'm telling you this for your sake.

663
00:43:08,935 --> 00:43:12,215
Consider him seriously just once.

664
00:43:12,215 --> 00:43:13,925
It's not just because he's a chaebol's son.

665
00:43:13,925 --> 00:43:15,715
He really is a good person.

666
00:43:15,715 --> 00:43:18,175
He really likes you sincerely.

667
00:43:18,175 --> 00:43:20,285
He'd care for you for the rest of his life, too.

668
00:43:20,285 --> 00:43:23,425
So, just once. Just once.

669
00:43:23,425 --> 00:43:29,125
Mom, I'll date someone I'm naturally drawn to.

670
00:43:29,125 --> 00:43:33,395
So don't mention President Gong to me from now on. Okay?

671
00:43:34,085 --> 00:43:36,015
I'm going to work.

672
00:43:37,615 --> 00:43:40,085
Gosh, you little...

673
00:43:40,935 --> 00:43:46,115
She'll date someone she's naturally drawn to?

674
00:43:46,115 --> 00:43:49,225
Gosh, is she seeing someone?

675
00:43:49,225 --> 00:43:53,055
Could it be Cha Bong Soo?

676
00:43:53,055 --> 00:43:57,575
Is Do Ra seeing someone by chance?

677
00:43:57,575 --> 00:44:00,825
Is she seeing someone? No, no. I don't think so.

678
00:44:00,825 --> 00:44:02,205
Really?

679
00:44:02,205 --> 00:44:05,025
How about Cha Bong Soo, then?

680
00:44:05,025 --> 00:44:08,995
People flirt when they shoot a romance. Anything like that?

681
00:44:08,995 --> 00:44:13,035
Things are better now, but they were enemies in the beginning.

682
00:44:13,035 --> 00:44:15,015
It's probably not Cha Bong Soo.

683
00:44:15,015 --> 00:44:17,465
There's no way, in my opinion.

684
00:44:17,465 --> 00:44:19,535
Really?

685
00:44:19,535 --> 00:44:22,535
President Baek, I need to go before her shoot ends.

686
00:44:22,535 --> 00:44:25,215
Okay, okay. You should go. You should go.

687
00:44:25,215 --> 00:44:30,635
Jae Dong, you need to keep a close tab on her, okay?

688
00:44:30,635 --> 00:44:31,995
I will.

689
00:44:31,995 --> 00:44:34,275
- Good luck today. 
 - Thank you.

690
00:44:35,325 --> 00:44:39,585
Mom, you've been quiet for a while. What's going on now?

691
00:44:39,585 --> 00:44:42,045
She's not a child anymore. Just leave her alone.

692
00:44:42,045 --> 00:44:44,555
So what if she's dating someone?

693
00:44:44,555 --> 00:44:48,575
Hey, we're about to become in-laws with APP Group.

694
00:44:48,575 --> 00:44:51,645
We're about to hit the jackpot right now. But you want me to do nothing?

695
00:44:51,645 --> 00:44:54,425
You think we'd get another chance like this?

696
00:44:54,425 --> 00:44:58,895
So, you're saying the chaebol, President Gong Jin Dan, likes Do Ra?

697
00:44:58,895 --> 00:45:01,005
Hello.

698
00:45:09,085 --> 00:45:13,265
How did Pil Sung turn out so well?

699
00:45:13,265 --> 00:45:15,695
Why is he so handsome?

700
00:45:18,415 --> 00:45:22,155
Oh, my! What are you doing? You decided not to do this.

701
00:45:22,155 --> 00:45:24,465
Get it together, Park Do Ra.

702
00:45:26,905 --> 00:45:30,965
Yes, I was so scared on the deserted island

703
00:45:30,965 --> 00:45:34,165
that I was relying on him. That's why I'm like this.

704
00:45:34,165 --> 00:45:38,425
Because of the pure memories of the 12-year-old Park Do Ra.

705
00:45:38,425 --> 00:45:41,975
Park Do Ra, keep your eyes peeled and watch carefully.

706
00:45:41,975 --> 00:45:44,775
That curly-haired man isn't handsome at all.

707
00:45:46,595 --> 00:45:48,005
Are you okay?

